title: Microsoft Pandora's Box
description: A box is opened. Pieces fly away. And seven mythical Tricksters escape to wreak havoc on the world. Welcome to Microsoft Pandora&#039;s Box, a puzzle-solving game that will take you literally to the ends of the earth.  This visually stunning journey includes hundreds of the most beautiful puzzles ever created. It&#039;s up to you to solve them, capture the Tricksters, and save the world from chaos.
